# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Whitelist .gitignore
#
# This folder doubles as (a) the local workspace where every Oscille repo is
# cloned and (b) the checkout of the `oscille/.github` org-meta repo.
#
# Strategy: ignore EVERYTHING at the root by default, then re-include only the
# org-meta files this repo is meant to track. Because `/*` matches only
# top-level entries (it does not cross `/`), any repo you clone in here is
# automatically ignored, with no per-repo maintenance and no risk of git trying
# to embed a nested clone as a stray gitlink.
#
# To track a new top-level file/dir, add a `!` negation below.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

/*

# Repo + workspace docs
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/CLAUDE.md
!/CONSTITUTION.md
!/LICENSE
!/conventions/

# GitHub org-wide defaults
!/profile/
!/.github/
!/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md
!/CONTRIBUTING.md
!/SECURITY.md
!/SUPPORT.md

# Brand / media kit
!/brand/

# Cloned repositories live here. Keep the folder, ignore the clones inside it.
!/repositories/
/repositories/*
!/repositories/.gitkeep

# Local-only notes (kept out of the published repo)
.DS_Store
